*   ## **_IWGP WORLD HEAVYWEIGHT CHAMPIONSHIP: TETSUYA NAITO(c) vs JON MOXLEY_**
    

The crowd was tired but the match was awesome.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bf26bb70-2f96-4e0a-b3be-f7692c00b47c/20240412_204307.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_WINNER: JON MOXLEY IS THE NEW IWGP WORLD HEAVYWEIGHT CHAMPION!!!_**
    

JON MOXLEY CALLS OUT SHOTA UMINO!

…but is then attacked by Ren Narita to close the show.